revision.text:
<!-- ConditionMapping for type of Person -->
{{ConditionalMapping
| cases =
 {{Condition
    | templateProperty = typeprijs
    | operator = contains
    | value = Natuurkunde
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Scientist
                }}

 }}

 {{Condition
    | templateProperty = typeprijs
    | operator = contains
    | value = Scheikunde
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Scientist
                }}

 }}

 {{Condition
    | templateProperty = typeprijs
    | operator = contains
    | value = Fysiologie
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Scientist
                }}

 }}

 {{Condition
    | templateProperty = typeprijs
    | operator = contains
    | value = Geneeskunde
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Scientist
                }}

 }}

 {{Condition
    | templateProperty = typeprijs
    | operator = contains
    | value = Literatuur
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Writer
                }}

 }}

<!-- 'otherwise', meestal Nobelprijs voor de Vrede of Prijs van de Zweedse Rijksbank voor economie -->
 {{Condition
    | operator = otherwise
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                | mapToClass = Person
                }}
 }}


<!-- DefaultMappings for every Person -->
| defaultMappings =
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = naam | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = afbeelding | ontologyProperty = picture }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = onderschrift | ontologyProperty = pictureDescription }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = land | ontologyProperty = country }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = geboorteplaats | ontologyProperty = birthPlace }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = plaatsvanoverlijden | ontologyProperty = deathPlace }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = nationaliteit | ontologyProperty = nationality }}
	{{DateIntervalMapping 
        | templateProperty = periode 
        | startDateOntologyProperty = birthDate 
        | endDateOntologyProperty = deathDate
    	}}


<!-- IntermediateNodeMapping for NobelPrize -->
	{{IntermediateNodeMapping
	| nodeClass = NobelPrize
	| correspondingProperty = award
	| mappings =
    	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = voor | ontologyProperty = predecessor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = voor2 | ontologyProperty = predecessor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = op | ontologyProperty = successor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = op2 | ontologyProperty = successor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = jaar | ontologyProperty = year }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = jaar2 | ontologyProperty = year }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = typeprijs | ontologyProperty = category }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = typeprijs2 | ontologyProperty = category }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = met | ontologyProperty = alongside }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = met2 | ontologyProperty = alongside }}
	}}
}}
